just run descriptormode without any arguments to get some basic usage.

OBSOLETE
~~~~~~~~
this still works, but is obsolted today (2013). this code and support
for more chipsets has been integrated into flashrom by Stefan Tauner
and others.

GOTO https://flashrom.org/Downloads

